      <title>美国与海湾盟国就针对胡塞武装采取军事行动进行谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-08/us-in-talks-with-gulf-allies-on-military-action-against-houthis</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据几位知情人士透露，美国一直在与海湾盟国就针对伊朗支持的也门胡塞叛军可能采取的军事行动进行磋商，以应对他们在红海对船只日益肆无忌惮的袭击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-08/us-in-talks-with-gulf-allies-on-military-action-against-houthis</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Dec 2023 18:16:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英特尔、强生和财政纪律帮助哥斯达黎加超越地区</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-08/intel-j-j-and-fiscal-discipline-help-costa-rica-outpace-region</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哥斯达黎加总统罗德里戈·查韦斯 (Rodrigo Chaves) 表示，随着财政前景改善有助于吸引投资，哥斯达黎加将在 2024 年保持经济势头，使其成为该地区的成功典范。]]></description>
